targets.expression:
fields @timestamp, @message
| parse @message "[*] [*] [*] [*] [*] [*] [transaction.id=*, trace.id=*, http_method=*, request_body=*, user_info=*, user_token=*, request_uri=*] *" as date, host, thread, level, package, class, transaction_id, trace_id, http_method, request_body, user_info, user_token, request_uri, body
| filter class not like /CommonsRequestLoggingFilter/
| filter request_uri != 'null'
| filter level = 'ERROR'
| sort @timestamp desc
| display @timestamp, level, class,  method, request_uri, user_token, request_body, user_info, body
| limit 30
